    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div">
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">緑</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">みどり</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の森がよろこびの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">声</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こえ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>で<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">笑</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">わら</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>い<lb />
波だつ小川が笑いながら<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">走</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ってゆく、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">空気</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くうき</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>までが私たちの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">愉快</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ゆかい</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>な<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">常談</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">じょうだん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>で笑い<lb />
緑の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">丘</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おか</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>がその声で笑い出す。<lb />
<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">牧場</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">まきば</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>がいきいきした緑で笑い<lb />
きりぎりすが<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">楽</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">たの</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>しい<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">景色</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">けしき</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の中で笑う、<lb />
メアリとスーザンとエミリとが<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">可愛</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かわい</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>い口をまるくしてハ・ハ・ヒと歌う。<lb />
<lb />
私たちが<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">桜</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さくら</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>んぼと<span rend="SESAME_DOT" rendition="strong">くるみ</span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">御馳走</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ごちそう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>をならべると<lb />
その<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">樹</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">き</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">蔭</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かげ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>できれいな鳥が笑っている、<lb />
さぁ元気で<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">愉快</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ゆかい</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に手をつなぎましょう<lb />
うれしいハ・ハ・ヒを<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">合唱</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">がっしょう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>しましょう。<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
